p: I, H.G. Thornton to whom the within warrant is dirrected, upon oath do say that I received the same for service on the 21st day of January, 1874 and served the same on the 22d day of January 1874, by arresting and taking under my custody at Port Madison, in Kitsap County, Washington Territory, Seo Kim the person named in said warrant while she was in the custody of and forcibly restrained of her liberty by her and Chinasman, to one who the and carry the said Seo Kim as I and believed, and now and of the Territory of Washington against her will.
Subscribed &Sworn to before me this 28h day of Jany 1874
